title: American Masters: Inventing David Geffen
description: The son of Jewish immigrants, David Geffen emerged from a humble upbringing to become one of the most powerful media personalities in America.

title: Bridgerton - The Afterparty
description: "Bridgerton" cast members share behind-the-scenes stories from the hit show, plus comedian Nikki Glaser breaks down the costume drama's sexiest moments.

title: Bling Empire - The Afterparty
description: The stars of "Bling Empire" discuss the show's success and play bling-themed games, then comic Joel Kim Booster makes his case for joining the cast.

title: Cobra Kai - The Afterparty
description: Ralph Macchio, William Zabka and more from the "Cobra Kai" cast drop by to chat Season 3 (spoilers ahead!), followed by Bill Burr of "F Is for Family."

title: To All the Boys: Always and Forever - The Afterparty
description: Cast members of the "To All the Boys" films dish about the third movie and answer some fan questions, plus Whitney Cummings gives suspect dating advice.

title: Fireplace 4K: Classic Crackling Fireplace from Fireplace for Your Home
description: The first of its kind in UHD 4K, with the clearest picture available, a real fireplace sparks and crackles, adding warmth and atmosphere to any home.

title: Fireplace 4K: Crackling Birchwood from Fireplace for Your Home
description: For the first time in 4K Ultra-HD, everyone's favorite Yuletide fireplace snaps and crackles in crystal clear, high-def holiday warmth.

title: Monster High: Electrified
description: Clawdeen wants to turn an abandoned power station into a salon for monsters and "normies" alike. But Moanica's got a shocking plan to ruin everything.

title: Justice
description: A U.S. Marshal arrives at a small town in Nevada, only to learn that his preacher brother is dead after standing up to the town's mayor and outlaws.

title: Night on Earth: Shot in the Dark
description: This look behind the scenes shows how worldwide camera crews climbed, dived and froze to capture the documentary's groundbreaking night footage.

title: 100 Things to do Before High School
description: Led by seventh-grader C.J., three students who have been warned about the dangers of high school decide to make the best of their middle-school years.

title: The House of Flowers Presents: The Funeral
description: The de la Mora siblings publicly mourn the death of their mother amid multiple surprises and mishaps at Virginia's funeral.

title: Lego DC Comics: Batman Be-Leaguered
description: When Superman and the other Justice League superheroes start disappearing, it's up to Batman to unravel the caper and save the day.

title: Aggretsuko: We Wish You a Metal Christmas
description: While Retsuko desperately makes plans for Christmas Eve, her new obsession with seeking validation through social media spirals out of control.

title: Oddbods: The Festive Menace
description: In this "Oddbods" special, Bubbles's latest invention, the Naughty-or-Nice Machine, zaps Santa Claus, jeopardizing the whole Christmas holiday season.

title: Club de Cuervos Presents: I, Potro
description: Former Club de Cuervos player Potro returns home to Argentina to crash the wedding of his famous soccer-star brother and confront his estranged family.

title: Derren Brown: Sacrifice
description: Illusionist Derren Brown concocts a psychological experiment in which he tries to manipulate an ordinary person into taking a bullet for a stranger.

title: Oddbods: Party Monsters
description: Dressed up as detective Sherlock Holmes, Slick must crack the case when a magician turns Jeff's spooky-costume party guests into their scary alter egos.

title: Da Kath & Kim Code
description: Kath and Kel's union is tested by Michael Bublé, daughter Kim tries pole dancing, pal Sharon finds love online, and a stalker lurks amid Yuletide cheer.

title: Pocoyo & Cars
description: Pocoyo gears up for exciting car races and learns that friends, teamwork and imagination are what matter the most.

title: Pocoyo & The Space Circus
description: Acrobatic aliens arrive on spaceships and perform for everyone, but when angry aliens arrive as well, Pocoyo and his friends must now put on a show.

title: Pocoyo Carnival
description: To celebrate the carnival, everyone learns to dance to different music. Plus, Pocoyo's friends surprise him with something delicious.

title: Pocoyo Halloween: Space Halloween
description: Pocoyo and his friends have a costume contest to celebrate Halloween and learn new things about planets and stars in space.

title: Pocoyo Halloween: Spooky Movies
description: Pocoyo finds a special toy and plays new games with his friends, then they’re spooked by a scary box and try to find out who’s inside.

title: Pocoyo Special Sports
description: Everyone is getting excited for the games. Pocoyo plays baseball and golf, and races with his friends. Ready, set, go!

title: Trailer Park Boys Live at the North Pole
description: Bubbles's plan to spread the true meaning of Christmas is dashed by Julian's wish to cash in on the holiday and Ricky's quest to meet the real Santa.

title: Trailer Park Boys Live In F**kin' Dublin
description: The boys head to Ireland after winning a contest to see Rush but are arrested by immigration and must perform a community service puppet show.

title: Trailer Park Boys: Xmas Special
description: See what Sunnyvale Trailer Park was like back in the day, featuring Randy as a prostitute, J-Roc before he rapped and Barb and Lahey still together.

title: Derren Brown: The Push
description: Mentalist Derren Brown engineers an audacious social experiment demonstrating how manipulation can lead an ordinary person to commit an appalling act.

title: Natascha Kampusch: The Whole Story
description: A Viennese child who was kidnapped and held captive in a basement before escaping after eight years reveals her headline-making story of survival.

title: Louis C.K. 2017
description: Louis C.K. muses on religion, eternal love, giving dogs drugs, email fights, teachers and more in a live performance from Washington, D.C.

title: A Christmas Special: Miraculous: Tales of Ladybug & Cat Noir
description: Parisian teen Marinette transforms herself into superhero Ladybug to find her lonely secret crush Adrien when he runs away from home at Christmas.

title: Santa Pac's Merry Berry Day
description: Pac aims to keep Berry Day the happiest day ever by unraveling a curious mystery about his parents and thwarting Betrayus's plan to capture Santa Pac.

title: Pac's Scary Halloween
description: When sinister Dr. Pacenstein schemes to swap bodies with Pac during a Halloween party, Spiral, Cyli and Count Pacula scramble to save their pal.

title: Louis C.K.: Hilarious
description: Emmy-winning comedy writer Louis C.K. brings his caustic wit to Milwaukee, offering up his unique and uncensored take on sex, parenting and more.

title: Louis C.K.: Live at the Comedy Store
description: The comic puts his trademark hilarious/thought-provoking spin on finding a bat in his kitchen, seeing rats having sex, Boston accents and dead pets.

title: Marco Polo: One Hundred Eyes
description: A defiant warrior-monk arrives at Kublai Khan's court in chains and soon earns his tragic nickname in this 30-minute origin story.

title: BoJack Horseman Christmas Special: Sabrina's Christmas Wish
description: It's Christmas, and BoJack wants nothing to do with it. Then Todd shows up with a giant candy cane and an old "Horsin' Around" Christmas episode.

title: 13TH: A Conversation with Oprah Winfrey & Ava DuVernay
description: Oprah Winfrey sits down with director Ava DuVernay to discuss her Oscar-nominated film, historical cycles of oppression and the broken prison system.

title: Chhota Bheem Aur Kaala Yodha
description: Finally released after being trapped in an ancient book for centuries, a wicked warrior sets out to conquer Dholakpur – but not if Bheem can help it!

title: Chhota Bheem Ka Troll Se Takkar
description: Trolls kidnap the king's daughters and overtake the kingdom of Messina. Can Bheem track them down and bring the princesses home?

title: Frozen Planet: On Thin Ice
description: David Attenborough journeys to both polar regions to investigate what rising temperatures will mean for the people and wildlife that live there.

title: Frozen Planet: The Epic Journey
description: Collecting highlights from the epic documentary series that explores the entire polar year and the inhabitants, from the north to the south.

title: Jake's Buccaneer Blast
description: Jake, Izzy, Cubby and Skully face off against the scheming Captain Hook in a race to find special treasures hidden all around Never Land.

title: LeapFrog: Numberland
description: With transport support from their magic car, Axel, the LeapFrog pets make a new friend named Max, who helps them learn counting skills in Numberland.

title: LeapFrog: Phonics Farm
description: Scout takes a magical trip to a farm where an alligator and other friendly critters teach him all about sounding out the letters of the alphabet.

title: Mark Gatiss: A Study in Sherlock
description: Mark Gatiss, who co-created “Sherlock” and plays Mycroft Holmes, discusses the show with Benedict Cumberbatch, Martin Freeman and others in the cast.

title: Nova: Ultimate Mars Challenge
description: With access to the scientists and engineers responsible for the Curiosity rover's on-the-ground experiments, NOVA captures its landing on Mars.

title: Pee-wee's Playhouse: Christmas Special
description: Amid an avalanche of stars, Pee-wee straps on his ice skates and glides into the holiday season with Christmas cards, carols ... and Charo.

title: Power Rangers Samurai: Christmas Together, Friends Forever (Christmas Special)
description: On Christmas Eve, as the teens at Shiba House reflect on their first year together, they get an unexpected lesson on the true spirit of the holidays.

title: Power Rangers Samurai: Party Monsters (Halloween Special)
description: On Halloween night, the creepiest creatures from the Netherworld trade war stories about their battles with the Samurai Power Rangers.

title: Power Rangers Super Megaforce: The Legendary Battle (Extended)
description: New footage augments the tale of the Rangers, who give their all to save Earth from Vrak and Emperor Mavro, as the Armada stages an epic final attack.

title: Power Rangers Super Samurai: Trickster Treat
description: When a Nighlok invades the Samurai Rangers' dreams and turns them into nightmares, the Rangers must figure out what is reality and what is illusion.

title: Shopkins: Chef Club
description: In this first full Shopkins movie, Peppa-Mint is the new Shoppie in town who stirs things up by hosting a team cooking competition.

title: Shopkins: Wild
description: Beloved movie star Scarletta Gateau visits Shopville and recruits the Shopkins for a quest through the jungle to the mysterious world of Pawville.

title: Shopkins: World Vacation
description: The Shopkins and Shoppies jet around the world in search of missing friend Kooky Cookie, a stolen diamond and more vloggable adventure.

title: World's Weirdest Homes
description: From a bubble-shaped palace to an island built on plastic bottles, tour the world’s most fantastically bizarre residences.
